          <para>Spare parts and tools 備品與工具</para>
          <para><internalRef internalRefId="小時HR" internalRefTargetType="irtt09"/></para>
          <para>2.3.1 Supply scope for spare parts 裝備供應商應提供之備品內容範圍</para>
          <para>The maker/supplier shall provide enough spare parts as follows：</para>
          <para>（1） In compliance with CR or ABS Classification Society Rules for ships with unrestricted service. (CR or ABS 船級協會無水域限制船舶備品量規定)<internalRef internalRefId="狗" internalRefTargetType="irtt09"/></para>
          <para>（2） 2-years on-board spare parts (艦上保養二年備品)</para>
          <para>A. The 2-years on-board spare parts will be loaded shipboard at ship delivery, and are intended to be used for maintenance by ship crews.</para>
          <para>艦上保養二年備品係提供艦上官兵執行週期性檢查、保養或更換之保養維修零附件。</para>
          <para>B. Based on technical manual and maker’s maintenance experience, spare parts (including but not limited to the following) which require to periodical check or change with maintenance intervals of every 1 month / 3 months</para>
          <para>/ 6 months / 12 months / 24 months, shall be provided by the supplier：</para>
          <para>(a) Cathodic protection zinc anodes or zinc pieces. (at least one set of spare anodes for each type) 防蝕鋅極或鋅塊。</para>
          <para>(b) Filter elements with seals. (At least one set of various types of spare</para>
          <para>filter elements shall be provided, including air filter, fuel filter, lubricating oil filter, hydraulic oil filter, fresh water filter, sea water filter, oil / water separating filter) 各類過濾器濾芯。</para>
          <para>(c) Belts (at least one set of spare belts for each type) 皮帶。</para>
          <para>(d) Mechanical seals (機械軸封)。(e) Grease (油脂)。</para>
          <para>(f) Others (其他)。</para>
          <para>The quantity shall meet two (2) years requirement of periodical check or change-out. The ship is estimated with 2000 operating hours per year.</para>
          <figureAlts>
            <figure>
              <title>狗</title>
              <graphic infoEntityIdent="ICN-SOIC-A-AEB59C-0-A-C50C-A" reproductionWidth="150mm"/>
            </figure>
          </figureAlts>
          <para id="小時HR">依據裝備技術手冊及裝備廠家保養維修作業經驗，將保養週期為(每日、每週、每月、每季、每半年、每年、每兩年)需週期性檢查或更換之保養維修零附件，(包括但不限於：防蝕鋅極或鋅塊、過濾器濾芯、皮帶、機械軸封、油脂)，裝備廠家/供應商應提供2年份定期檢查或更換所需備用數量。本船預估每年執行任務操作時數2000小時。</para>
